          <Card className="p-6 bg-yellow-100">
            <h3 className="font-semibold text-lg">üìä ‡∏™‡∏ñ‡∏¥‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô</h3>
            <p className="text-gray-600">‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô 24 ‡∏Ñ‡∏ô</p>
          </Card>
          <Card className="p-6 bg-pink-100">
            <h3 className="font-semibold text-lg">‚è≥ ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ</h3>
